Hit-tiap8 mng5-sin5, thou2-ti7-kong, chai5-sin5, be2-sin5, gu5-ong5, chui2-chhau2 tai7-ong5, long2 chhut-goa7 iu5-oan2, bo5 loa7-ku2 chiong3 ke-sin5 tang5-che5 to3--lai5, khoaN3-kiN3 sin5-ui7 long2 khang-khang, chiaN3-chiaN3 tiu5-tu5 teh siuN7, m7-chai sim2-mih8 in-toaN. Hut-jian5 thiaN-kiN3 pang5-keng teh jiang2-nau2, chiu7 khi3 chha5-kho2, goan5-lai5 khiok si7 in-ui7 chit8-e5 kiong5-kui2 chai7 ka chok-chong7, chiaN3 beng5-pek8, cheng3 sin5-beng5 chit-si5 ia7 siu7-khi3, tui3 kiong5-kui2 hoah kong2 chit8-si3 bo5 ti7-teh. Li2 thai3 ho2-taN2, jia2-chhut che toa7 ho7-toan, ti3-kau3 hai7 goan2, bo5 tang3 i-oa2 e5 te7-ui7? Liam5-piN kio3 te7-hng-kui2 eng7 thih-lian7 chiong kiong5-kui2 pak8--khi3, ke3-sang3 kau3 Seng7-hong5-ia5 bin7-thau5-cheng5, phah sou2-pah-e7 pan2-poe, koh gia5 chit8 bin7 ke5 so2 ti7 bio7-khau2 si7-chiong3. 
U7 chit8 jit8 pu3-kui2 kiaN5 kau3 seng7-hong5-bio7 khau2, khoaN3-kiN3 kiong5-kui2 gia5 thau5-ho7-ke5 ti7-hia, mng7 kong2, Ai3-te7 hoan7 sim2-mih8 choe7, gia5-ke5 koaN7-so2? Kiong5-kui2 lau5 bak8-sai2 kong2, chiong-cheng5 Jin5-hiaN ka3 goa2 hoat-chai5 e5 ho2 hong-hoat, gu5-te7 chiau3 lau2-ko e5 oe7 khi3 kiaN5. SiaN3 chai biau2-si7-kui2 hit-ho7-lang5, kian-sim m7 sin3, m7 na7 bo5 beh hian3 choa2-be2 gin5-chiN5, hoan2-tng2 chiong mng5-sin5 thou2-ti7 kap cheng3 sin5-beng5 e5 sin5-siong7 chip8 che5 sio-hoe2 siak phoa3, ti3-kau3 chhiok-hoan7 cheng3 Sin5-beng5 siu7-khi3, kio3 te7-hong-kui2 lai5 khun2-pak8 goa2, ke3-sang3 kau3 Seng5-hong5-ia5 bin7-cheng5, pan2-poe phah liau2, iu7 gia5 ke5 tiam3 chia. ThiaN lau2-ko e5 oe7, pun2 ui7-tioh8 beh kiu5 hoat-chai5, tian-to3 koh khah chham2. Pu3-kui2 thiaN-liau2, ki2 kiong5-kui2 me7 kong2, bok8-koai3 li2 tioh8 pin5-kiong5, gia5-ke5 ia7 bo5 khek-khui, li2 lian7 chhong-beng5 kian3-siat to bo5, hoan2-tng2 oan3-hin7 goa2. Ki3-jian5 beh jip8 jin5-ke chok-chong7, tai7-seng tioh8 khoaN3 hit ke u7 sin3 kui2 a2 bo5; na7 m7 sin3 chiu7-tioh8 hng7-hng7 siam2-pi7, bian2-tit thoa-lui7 siu7-khou2. 
